description:
We all know Omni Man is pretty OP, but let’s talk about someone who is arguably one of the MOST POWERFUL heroes in the Invincible universe: Atom Eve. Able to control matter with the blink of an eye, Atom Eve has the power to turn everyday objects into SOLID 24K GOLD. While that may seem like a good thing, it could lead to some catastrophic consequences…
